2026-05-15T04:49:05.7103903Z 12    <!--
2026-05-15T04:49:05.7104311Z 13        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-15T04:49:05.7104670Z 14        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-05-15T04:49:05.7105376Z 15        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-05-15T04:49:05.7105744Z 16        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-05-15T04:49:05.7106152Z 17        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
